 {"id":"bd-3ty3s","title":"epic(recipe-B): Tail-Safe Adaptive Controller (Composition Recipe)","description":"Graveyard Composition Recipe B: Adaptive behavior without p99 regression. Primitives: Expected-loss (S0.4) + Conformal (S12.1, already impl) + E-processes (S0.18, already impl) + Drift detection (S0.14, BOCPD already impl). MISSING: unified expected-loss layer, SOS barrier guard, policy-as-data bundle. Safe-mode: deterministic conservative policy (full diff, no coalescing, no degradation). This recipe unifies what FrankenTUI already has into a coherent tail-safe system.\n\n**User Value:** Guarantees that adaptive rendering never exceeds frame budget, with automatic fallback to safe mode if p99 latency spikes.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- Conformal prediction wrapper on frame timing\n- Automatic degradation when p99 exceeds budget\n- Evidence ledger emits on every fallback\n- Recovery to full mode when tail stabilizes\n- All existing tests pass","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-02-13T21:50:33.239744430Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T23:09:39.414161484Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["alien","graveyard","recipe","statistics"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ty3s","depends_on_id":"bd-1d3z0","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:26:01Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3ty3s","depends_on_id":"bd-3rss7","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:26:01Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3ty3s","depends_on_id":"bd-fp38v","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:26:01Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-3ty3s.1","title":"task(e2e): E2E test suite for Recipe B Tail-Safe Adaptive","description":"## E2E Integration Test: Recipe B Tail-Safe Adaptive Controller (EV=recipe)\n\n### Scope\nFull integration test inducing drift, verifying fallback triggers, and logging conformal/e-process/BOCPD convergence. Validates p99 stays bounded under all conditions.\n\n### Test Scenario\n1. Initialize FrankenTUI with Recipe B controller active (expected-loss + conformal + e-process + BOCPD).\n2. Phase 1 - Steady state (frames 0-100): stable 60fps, verify adaptive behavior.\n3. Phase 2 - Gradual drift (frames 100-200): slowly increase frame times from 8ms to 18ms.\n4. Verify BOCPD detects changepoint within 20 frames of drift onset.\n5. Verify e-process crossing triggers sequential test alarm.\n6. Verify conformal prediction intervals widen to accommodate drift.\n7. Phase 3 - Fallback (frames 200-250): verify safe-mode activates (deterministic conservative policy: full diff, no coalescing, no degradation).\n8. Phase 4 - Recovery (frames 250-350): drift reverses, verify controller re-adapts.\n9. Throughout all phases: verify p99 frame time stays < 20ms (tail-safe guarantee).\n\n### JSONL Structured Logging Specification\nEach frame emits:\n```json\n{\n  \"event\": \"recipe_b_frame\",\n  \"ts_ns\": u64,\n  \"frame_id\": u64,\n  \"phase\": \"steady|drift|fallback|recovery\",\n  \"conformal_interval\": { \"lower\": f64, \"upper\": f64 },\n  \"conformal_coverage\": f64,\n  \"e_process_value\": f64,\n  \"e_process_crossed\": bool,\n  \"bocpd_run_length\": u32,\n  \"bocpd_changepoint_prob\": f64,\n  \"expected_loss_action\": \"string\",\n  \"safe_mode_active\": bool,\n  \"frame_time_ms\": f64,\n  \"p99_frame_time_ms\": f64,\n  \"p99_bounded\": bool\n}\n```\n\n### Success Criteria\n- BOCPD detects drift within 20 frames of onset (changepoint_prob > 0.8).\n- E-process crosses threshold during drift phase.\n- Safe mode activates before p99 exceeds 20ms.\n- p99_bounded == true for ALL frames (the tail-safe guarantee).\n- Recovery phase re-enables adaptive behavior within 50 frames.\n- No panics, no unsafe code (#![forbid(unsafe_code)]).\n- JSONL log is schema-compliant and parseable.\n- Conformal coverage maintains >= 95% throughout test.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T22:26:15.812899903Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T23:09:25.749785273Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["e2e","logging","test"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ty3s.1","depends_on_id":"bd-3ty3s","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:26:01Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-3ty3s.1","depends_on_id":"bd-3ty3s.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:26:01Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
